title: Alien Encounters - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 3/14/22

description:
George Noory and UCLA professor Dr. David Shorter discuss his father's experience working on secret government UFO projects, growing up with a psychic grandmother, and recounts a chilling eyewitness report of recovering dying alien bodies from a UFO crash in New Mexico.
